text: Castell'Anselmo is a village in Tuscany, central Italy, administratively a frazione of the comune of Collesalvetti, province of Livorno. At the time of the 2011 census its population was 234. The village is about 16 km from Livorno and 5 km from Collesalvetti. == Bibliography == * Category:Frazioni of the Province of Livorno
title: Castell'Anselmo
